summary.label:
Explore Ugly Duckling's interactive children's fairy tale and try augmented reality games with the story's animated characters. 

With AR Market the classic Ugly Duckling fable is interactive. Besides listening to the story in multilanguage, you can play with the characters in augmented reality. You can move the Ugly Duckling through the maze to find the exit, or you can blow the frog into the pond! You can also use the photo filter and turn yourself into a beautiful swan. With this app every occasion is good to learn and play in an innovative way. 

The app is designed by AR MARKET for children from 3 to 6 years old.

Main features: 
- Classin fairy tale in 5 languages (Italian, English, French, Spanish and German);
- 3D games and augmented reality;
- Animated characters;
- Interactive scenes; 
- Colors and sounds designed for children;
- Develop children's imagination and knowledge;
- Easy and fun to use. 

Discover the fairytale now. Play with it and listen to it! 

The App does not collect any user data and it respects the privacy policy (refer to AR MArket privacy policy at URL reported).
